value: Time to work off the sweets.
As great as a new outfit sounds, what I really want right now is some crème brûlée...
Hey, I'm watching those hands, pal! You're not picking any candy from these pockets.
Múspell is the Kingdom of Flame, right? I better leave the chocolate at home then, or I'll end up in a sticky situation...
I appreciate the new clothes, but don't blame me if they get dirty on the job.
There are some pretty intimidating Heroes in Múspell. I better keep my distance. You know, for the sake of the sweets...and for my own sake, I guess.
Nobody is asking the essential questions about these clothes... For starters, how many pockets does this getup have?
I take my sweets very seriously... You'll know you're on my good side when I offer to share with you.
